Matplotlib - Theory in Hinglish:
🔹 Matplotlib ek Python library hai jo data ko visually represent karne ke liye use hoti hai, especially graphs aur charts banane ke liye.

🔹 Ye mainly 2D plotting ke liye famous hai, aur scientific graphs banane ke liye widely use hoti hai.

🔹 Iska main module pyplot hai, jisko generally import matplotlib.pyplot as plt ke naam se import karte hain.

📊 Commonly Used Plot Types:
Line Plot – data points ko line se jodta hai.
plt.plot(x, y)

Bar Chart – categorical data ke liye.
plt.bar(x, height)

Histogram – data ke distribution ko dikhata hai.
plt.hist(data)

Scatter Plot – 2 variables ke relation ko show karta hai.
plt.scatter(x, y)

Pie Chart – percentage ya proportion dikhata hai.
plt.pie(data)

🛠️ Important Functions:
plt.title() → Graph ka title set karta hai.

plt.xlabel() / plt.ylabel() → X aur Y axis ka label set karta hai.

plt.legend() → Graph ke elements ka label show karta hai.

plt.grid() → Graph mein grid lines add karta hai.

plt.show() → Graph ko screen pe show karta hai.

